N = int(input())
a = []
for i in range(N):
    a.append([int(x) for x in input().split()])

for i in range(N):
    for j in range(N):
        if i == j:
            a[i][j] = 0

for i in range(N):
    for j in range(N):
        if a[i][j] == 0:
            continue
        for k in range(N):
            if a[i][k] == a[k][j]:
                a[i][j] = a[i][k]
                break
            else:
                a[i][j] = 0

for i in range(N):
    for j in range(N):
        if a[i][j] != 0:
            a[i][j] = a[i][j] | a[i][i]

for i in range(N):
    for j in range(N):
        print(a[i][j], end=" ")
    print()
